-- London’s Shard in Talks With Potential Tenants, Telegraph Says
-- B y   Z i j i n g   W u
-- 2012-07-01T08:31:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-01/london-s-shard-in-talks-with-potential-tenants-telegraph-says.html
The Shard, London’s new landmark
building, is in “serious talks” with three potential office
tenants, the Sunday Telegraph reported, citing  Irvine  Sellar,
chairman of the building’s developer Sellar Property Group. The
Shard will have its formal inauguration on July 5, the paper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
